==============================================================
		calipso httpd SAPI module
==============================================================

1) This is an EXPERIMENTAL sapi - may be changed soon.

NOTE:
	CALIPSO module is only usable in thread-safe mode

2) TESTING with php 5.1.2, 5.1.4 - 5.2.9 

3) Calipso SAPI quick hack:
	- untar calipso0xx-sapi.bz2 this produce folder with 
	name calipso
	
	- download last php5 source from http://php.net/

	- put folder calipso int the _php_src_dir/sapi

	- run ./buildconf --force

	- run 	./configure, something like this:
Example:
	./configure --with-mysql --enable-force-cgi-redirect\
	--disable-cgi --with-zlib --with-gettext --with-gdbm\
	--with-calipso=~/calipso-svn/src

4) make install or make install-sapi

